org.openlcb

Class SimpleNodeIdent

Show UML class diagram
  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openlcb.SimpleNodeIdent

  • public class SimpleNodeIdent
extends Object
    Accumulates data from Simple Node Ident Protocol replies and provides access to the resulting data to represent a single node.
    See Also:
    "http://www.openlcb.org/trunk/specs/drafts/GenSimpleNodeInfoS.pdf", "http://www.openlcb.org/trunk/specs/drafts/GenSimpleNodeInfoTN.pdf"
